==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Decern
<hw>De*cern"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>decernere</ets>. See <er>Decree</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To
perceive, discern, or decide.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Granmer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>To decree; to
adjudge.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 376 --></p>

<p><ent>Decerniture</ent>⟦br⟧
